&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skip this step if unnecessary, and proceed to create a certificate pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;certificate-pipeline&#34;&gt;Certificate Pipeline
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2025050101/QQ_1746084517963.png&#34;
