&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Click to create a new pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2025050101/QQ_1746084554706.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1328&#34;
	height=&#34;944&#34;
	srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/post/2025050101/QQ_1746084554706_hu_b488234289002ec2.png 480w, http://localhost:1313/post/2025050101/QQ_1746084554706_hu_31adc6ce6d719fd1.png 1024w&#34;
